Class AbstractMultiRunOutputDataset

java.lang.Object
  org.jamsim.ascape.output.AbstractMultiRunOutputDataset
All Implemented Interfaces:
MultiRunOutputDatasetProvider, OutputDatasetProvider
Direct Known Subclasses:
ROutputMultiRun, StatsRows
public abstract class AbstractMultiRunOutputDataset
extends Object
implements MultiRunOutputDatasetProvider

Implementation of MultiRunOutputDatasetProvider based on an array of doubles. Constructs a single run from the values provided by getValues(int) and getValueNames(). Constructs a multiple run dataset from all getValues(int) calls made.

getMultiRunDataset

public net.casper.data.model.CDataCacheContainer getMultiRunDataset()
                                                             throws net.casper.data.model.CDataGridException
Return dataset of collector function values from all runs. i.e: all calls to getValues(int). First column is provided by getValueNames(), and then each following column is a particular run, eg: Run 1, Run 2, Run 3 ...etc.
